<div class="activity" style="background-color: darksalmon">
    <div class="activity-title text-white" style="font-family: Eusthalia Sans Slant; font-size: 100px;font-style: italic; position:relative; padding-top: 20px; padding-left: 5%">
        <p>ACTIVITY</p>
    </div>
    <div class="card-columns" style="margin: auto; margin-top: -100px; width: 85%; padding: 10px;position: relative">
        <div class="card">
            <img class="card-img-top" src="~/Content/Image/yoga.jpeg" alt="Card image cap">
            <div class="card-body">
                <h5 class="card-title">Yoga</h5>
                <p class="card-text">Energize, unwind and realign with GoodLife’s Yoga Classes. Built on a foundation of strength and stability, each class utilizes key movements to promote proper body alignment, mobility and core strength, leaving you feeling calm and centered.</p>
                <a href="/Home/Activity" class="btn btn-primary">Drop in</a>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="card p-3">
            <div class="card-body">
                <h5 class="card-title">Steam Room / Sauna</h5>
                <p class="card-text">Nothing feels better after workout than resting your muscles in hot sauna or steam room. You come with full access to our facilities.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
            <img class="card-img-top" src="~/Content/Image/child.jpg" alt="Card image cap">
            <div class="card-body">
                <h5 class="card-title">Kids fitness</h5>
                <p class="card-text">Kids this age need physical activity to build strength, coordination, and confidence — and to lay the groundwork for a healthy lifestyle. They're also gaining more control over how active they are.</p>
                <a href="/Home/Activity" class="btn btn-primary">Drop in</a>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="card bg-primary text-white text-center p-3">
            <blockquote class="blockquote mb-0">
                <p>‘Let’s Move for a Better World’ </p>
                <footer class="blockquote-footer">
                    <small>
                        Someone famous in <cite title="Source Title">Source Title</cite>
                    </small>
                </footer>
            </blockquote>
        </div>
        <div class="card text-center">
            <div class="card-body">
                <h5 class="card-title">Towel Service</h5>
                <p class="card-text">Every location features full towel service, so you can feel free to travel light! We help make it even easier to fit your workouts into your busy life.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
            <img class="card-img" src="~/Content/Image/old.jpg" alt="Card image">
        </div>
        <div class="card p-3">
            <h5 class="card-title">Family Fitness Classes</h5>
            <p class="card-text">Family Fitness offers a fun fitness programme for parents and guardians and their older children or teens. This class is a great way to spend time together as a family. It also encourages the younger participants to develop lifelong fitness habits.</p>
            <a href="/Home/Activity" class="btn btn-primary">Drop in</a>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
            <div class="card-body">
                <h5 class="card-title">Red Light Therapy</h5>
                <p class="card-text">Red Light Therapy involves emitting red, low-light wavelengths through the skin to stimulate cellular rejuvenation, increase blood flow, stimulate collagen.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="coach" style="background-color: darkorange">
