<div class="review" style="background-color: coral ">
    <div class="review-title text-white" style="font-family: Eusthalia Sans Slant; font-size: 100px;font-style: italic; position:relative; padding-top: 20px; padding-left: 35%">
        <p>REVIEW</p>
    </div>
    <div class="card-deck" style="margin: auto;margin-top: -100px; width: 85%; padding: 10px; position: relative">
        <div class="card">
            <div class="card-body">
                <h5 class="card-title">Marko S.</h5>
                <p class="card-text">
                    Great location
                    Nice size gym
                    I will definitely be back again
                    Cardio equipment was great as well as the staff greeted me with a big smile, which goes a loooong way for me...

                    Thank you Motivators:)
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="card-footer">
                <p class="card-text text-sm-right">6/18/2019</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
            <div class="card-body">
                <h5 class="card-title">David J.</h5>
                <p class="card-text">
                    Good Gym that should have everything you need.
                    The personal training sections upstairs and downstairs take up alot of real estate all members could use. It can feel crowded especially after work times. The Sauna doesn't seem to work properly it never gets hot enough. The Price of a membership isn't cheap. Overall if it's convenient for you I would still recommend this gym
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="card-footer">
                <p class="card-text text-sm-right">2/4/2018</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
            <div class="card-body">
                <h5 class="card-title">Patrick D.</h5>
                <p class="card-text">
                    This is one of the better locations in the city. It's spacious and there is plenty of machines to use. The classrooms are a nice size, and the best part: it's 24 hours during the week (closes at 8pm Saturday and Sunday)

                    The Good:

                    1. Space. There is plenty of space to go around, especially during off hours.
                    2. Equipment. Again, there is plenty of equipment in this gym and its up to date and I've never seen any broken.
                    3. Staff. This differs from other locations in that staff are actually pleasant here. Lots of gyms have terrible customer service but this is not one of them.

                    The Bad:

                    1. Busy. This place gets extremely busy during the week in the peak hours (lunch time and after work). This is especially true for classes. You need to be here early to get a space.

                    Recommendation: go during off hours. You don't want to gain wait!
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="card-footer">
                <p class="card-text text-sm-right">1/18/2015</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="review-botton" style="display:block;margin:0 auto;width: 35%;padding-top: 50px; padding-bottom: 50px">
        <button type="button" class="btn btn-outline-light btn-block"><a href="/Home/Review" style="text-decoration:none; color:white">Write a new review</a></button>
    </div>
</div>

